{"tid":2413013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《狂舞派3》全用廣東話字幕, 搵專研廣東話團體校對","createTime":"2021-02-18T11:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T08:06:19.000Z","uid":134071,"like":807,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"38b4988075ae593b58bedaa656c5f4c86f21d8f6","tid":2413013,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:14:22.000Z","msg":"未睇套戲，但要讚套戲都好有心捍衛廣東話文化.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />. <br />\n而家，好少香港上映電影用全港東話字幕。（美國電影就更加少，因為美國片商多數會ban香港字幕中既大部分廣東話口語，Sausage Party係少數例外奇蹟。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/3828844407172256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fposts%2F3828844407172256&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69NVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=c08e2708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/3828844407172256</a><br />\n<br />\n今日（18號）喺政府放寬限聚令下，電影院都終於開返，備受注目嘅本地電影《狂舞派3》久候多時都喺今日首映。製片商高先電影總經理陳靜透露，今次電影係有個有趣設定：「我哋會全用廣東話字幕。」<br />\n<br />\n佢又話：「其實早喺80年代港產片都係用廣東話字幕，今次我哋更搵到一間專門研究廣東話嘅團體幫手校對。」但就未有透露係邊個團體幫手校對。"},{"pid":"786faf20d0dcd422ce5972c9fd44e83e012b98a0","tid":2413013,"uid":134071,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:14:44.000Z","msg":"支持廣東話文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcb16d03fe0a5fef057a982a890b2b3187bfe9b","tid":2413013,"uid":8308,"like":163,"dislike":1,"score":162,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:16:22.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n根本唔應該文言分離"},{"pid":"2ec8f7464aa11466f1254911062d95cc9f3a7977","tid":2413013,"uid":134071,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"真實事件：<br />\n<br />\n有一套美國三級片，原本英文粗口好多，但美國片商依然ban左字幕中大部分廣東話口語粗口。。。。"},{"pid":"230a33408ee03bdd675ab899a2f385aacf51ccd3","tid":2413013,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8bcb16d03fe0a5fef057a982a890b2b3187bfe9b","tid":2413013,"uid":8308,"like":1