:0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:14:22.000Z","msg":"未睇套戲，但要讚套戲都好有心捍衛廣東話文化.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />. <br />\n而家，好少香港上映電影用全港東話字幕。（美國電影就更加少，因為美國片商多數會ban香港字幕中既大部分廣東話口語，Sausage Party係少數例外奇蹟。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/3828844407172256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fposts%2F3828844407172256&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69NVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=c08e2708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/3828844407172256</a><br />\n<br />\n今日（18號）喺政府放寬限聚令下，電影院都終於開返，備受注目嘅本地電影《狂舞派3》久候多時都喺今日首映。製片商高先電影總經理陳靜透露，今次電影係有個有趣設定：「我哋會全用廣東話字幕。」<br />\n<br />\n佢又話：「其實早喺80年代港產片都係用廣東話字幕，今次我哋更搵到一間專門研究廣東話嘅團體幫手校對。」但就未有透露係邊個團體幫手校對。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T00:13:34.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"d256866aae511f283cec3dfbb015afc413448c32","tid":2413013,"uid":281584,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"5849ea8a043cb54e5f4e6d22cb2faaba95f5da35","tid":2413013,"uid":356010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"消失的第二集去咗邊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T00:22:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YQitIfz7ewc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYQitIfz7ewc&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69NVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=e9d92cfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YQitIfz7ewc</a>"},{"pid":"1201f8bfc7a66e1532158434b546711b616df01a","tid":2413013,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5849ea8a043cb54e5f4e6d22cb2faaba95f5da35","tid":2413013,"uid":356010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"消失的第二集去咗邊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T00:26:11.000Z","msg":"拍咗啦，試當真到"},{"pid":"5a7367c5d4602b3de34e1355bb96b3e8b52b66d8","tid":2413013,"uid":74302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1edd8084e3106f9d77e71cf4650d87667d7ac9de","tid